title: VPFL: coaches and draft change
author: VD
content_html:
A slight change of plans… the VPFL draft is Fri Sep 1 4:15pm central. League ID is 615400 and the following individuals should email me for the password:

Nate
The White Buffalo
Sean
Shrubbery
Supernaut
Waterboy
Someboed
TViper
Viking







Zek, Jim Jewell, Hold the Sky and Josh are first in line for next year’s VPFL… they’ll also be on tap in case anyone has to drop out. I’m sorry about the draft change, but I accidentally scheduled it at the same time as my main league’s draft.
